3.3 Operational Requirements

· All‑weather day/night operation.
· Autonomous takeoff and landing from unprepared surfaces.
· In‑flight refueling compatible.
· Operate in GPS‑denied environments.
· Nuclear, biological, chemical (NBC) survivable.

3.4 Environmental Requirements

· Temperature: -40°C to +55°C.
· Vibration: MIL‑STD‑810G.
· EMI/EMC: MIL‑STD‑461G.

