6. Interfaces

6.1 Internal Interfaces

· Sensor Data Bus: High‑speed serial (10 Gbps Ethernet) connecting sensors to compute.
· Actuator Bus: CAN FD for flight control surfaces.
· Power Bus: 270 VDC and 28 VDC with power management controllers.

6.2 External Interfaces

· Ground Control Station (GCS): IP‑based link via SATCOM or direct LOS, using STANAG 4586 (or equivalent) for command and control.
· Other UAVs/UCAVs: Mesh network for cooperative engagement.
· Command Center: Link 16 and SATCOM for strategic coordination.
· Air Traffic Control: ADS‑B out, voice relay.

