7. Modes of Operation

Mode Description
Takeoff/Landing Autonomous or remote‑controlled, using INS/GPS and vision.
Loiter (Surveillance) Electric propulsion, wings extended, sensors active.
Cruise Ramjet powered, wings swept, high‑speed transit.
